| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3825 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 74fc51d1-a208-5a11-8ec8-85f7fa490847"
